.Dd December 25, 2021
.Dt KSSCANF 9
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ksscanf ,
.Nm kvsscanf
.Nd input format conversion
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In sys/types.h
.In sys/systm.h
.Ft int
.Fn ksscanf "const char *str" "const char *format" ...
.Ft int
.Fn kvsscanf "const char *str" "const char *format" "__va_list ap"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn ksscanf
and
.Fn kvsscanf
functions are similar to the
.Xr sscanf 3
and
.Xr vsscanf 3
functions and handle the
.Fa format ,
.Fa str
and
.Fa ap
parameters in the same manner as these, as well as return values.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr scanf 3
